Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.78,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need to live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.75,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.03,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.93,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.94,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:53.81,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:54.32,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.97,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.02,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:05.17,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:11.77,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:01.83,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带刺的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:04.18,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你的故事里认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:09.19,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨之深皆因爱之切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:14.70,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为一己之利置朋友于死地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.19,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为了他人而牺牲自我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.33,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们又有何区别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:25.59,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！人生就是生存游戏　你要如何开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:31.09,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间和空间是分岔路口　你要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.62,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻求永生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.78,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但生存的意义又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.75,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不知道世界的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.03,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是时空的乱入者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.93,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不会因你而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.94,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则才决定着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:53.81,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我们凭着爱穿越古今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:54.32,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.97,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.02,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:05.17,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奇迹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:11.77,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是终结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.01,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:58.05,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動許される?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:09.35,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会いたくて涙 溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:22.57,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる身体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:34.98,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.01,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟还要失去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:58.05,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这剧烈的心悸方能被宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:09.35,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要见到你 想到热泪盈眶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.95,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是连接着未来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:22.57,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到崩坏身体的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:34.98,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意 再一次守护你 许下誓言
